      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>A bill to amend the Marine Mammal Protection Act of 1972 to allow the importation of polar bear trophies taken in sport hunts in Canada before the date on which the polar bear was determined to be a threatened species under the Endangered Species Act of 1973.</title>
      </item>
